details.description: Delegator have access through having one of the following role(s) for the reportee party: urn:altinn:rolecode:DAGL. Note: if the user is a Main Administrator (HADM) the user might not have direct access to the role other than for delegation purposes.
The fromParty has the right based on Access List delegation
